Is Restoration Hardware owned by Pottery Barn?

RH is an upscale American home-furnishings company headquartered in Corte Madera, California. The company sells its merchandise through its retail stores, catalog, and online. As of August, 2018, the company operated a total of 70 galleries, 18 full line design galleries, and 6 baby & child galleries.
